Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: CLI-based AI programming tool with local knowledge base
 Codex is a CLI-based AI programming tool that provides:
  - Local code knowledge base with Tantivy search engine
  - Remote web scraping capabilities
  - Multi-AI platform support (OpenAI, Claude, Ollama)
  - Code generation and explanation
  - Interactive chat interface
  - Task management system
 .
 Codex helps developers with code understanding, generation, and optimization,
 leveraging both local knowledge and remote AI capabilities.
